This is a module to serve Mercurial from web servers (hgweb) and accept changesets (via SSH).

Example usage:
node "hgweb.example.com" {
    include hg::webhead
}


# Note: Please don't use the SSH class, it's not tested yet.

node "hgssh.example.com" {
    include hg
    include hg::ssh
}

